{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778982461580,"sessionID":"ses_1cc61f63cffe3JDoCmXU5s6B5T","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_QTrJyBhk27Imoh8MNYcxoKgq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":400},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"This term has no enzyme xref:\\n\\nid: GO:0045550\\nname: geranylgeranyl reductase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the formation of phytyl group from the stepwise reduction of a geranylgeranyl group.\\\" [PMID:9492312]\\nis_a: GO:0016491 ! oxidoreductase activity\\n\\nPMID:9492312 abstract says:\\n\\\"Geranylgeranyl reductase expressed in Escherichia coli sequentially catalyzes the reduction of geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlorophyll a as well as the reduction of free geranylgeranyl diphosphate into phytyl diphosphate.\\\"\\n\\nBoth these reactions are covered by EC:1.3.1.83, whose entry says:\\nReaction catalysed: phytyl diphosphate + 3 NADP(+) = geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H(+)\\nComments: This enzyme also acts on geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a.\\n\\nThis is consistent with the MetaCyc entry for this gene (also attributed to PMID:9492312): https://metacyc.org/gene?orgid=META&id=AT1G74470-MONOMER#REFS\\n\\nSo:\\n- [x] GO:0045550 should be obsoleted and replaced with GO:0102067:\\n\\nid: GO:0102067\\nname: geranylgeranyl diphosphate reductase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: (E)-3,7,11,15-tetramethylhexadec-2-en-1-yl diphosphate + 3 NADP = 2-trans,6-trans,10-trans-geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H+.\\\" [EC:1.3.1.83, GOC:pz]\\nxref: EC:1.3.1.83 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-10625\\nxref: RHEA:26229 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nis_a: GO:0016628 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-CH group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor\\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \\\"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30193\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\n\\nThere are only 3 annotations to GO:0045550 geranylgeranyl reductase activity:\\n- human [AKR1C3](https://amigo.geneontology.org/amigo/gene_product/UniProtKB:P42330) by UP\\n- human [AKR1B10](https://amigo.geneontology.org/amigo/gene_product/UniProtKB:O60218) by UP\\n- Arabidopsis [CHLP](https://amigo.geneontology.org/amigo/gene_pr... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAoTt7g\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please update GO:0102067 definition according to sjm41 comments. Do not close this ticket. Obsoletion is to be completed later.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T16:34:47Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n16:         {\n17:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n18:           \"users\": {\n19:             \"totalCount\": 1\n20:           }\n21:         }\n22:       ],\n23:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963#issuecomment-4337233390\",\n24:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n25:     },\n26:     {\n27:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAoT3Qg\",\n28:       \"author\": {\n29:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n30:       },\n31:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n32:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25065339565)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n33:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T16:35:11Z\",\n34:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n35:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n36:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n37:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n38:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963#issuecomment-4337235778\",\n39:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n40:     },\n41:     {\n42:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAocGOQ\",\n43:       \"author\": {\n44:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n45:       },\n46:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n47:       \"body\": \"Updated the definition of GO:0102067 per @sjm41's comments. PR: #32006.\\n\\nSpecifically:\\n- Reaction simplified to use `phytyl diphosphate` and `geranylgeranyl diphosphate` to match the EC:1.3.1.83 / RHEA:26229 wording (`phytyl diphosphate + 3 NADP+ = geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H+`).\\n- `NADP` corrected to `NADP+`.\\n- Added a sentence noting that the enzyme also catalyzes the reduction of geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlorophyll a (per PMID:9492312).\\n- Definition references updated to `[EC:1.3.1.83, PMID:9492312, RHEA:26229]`.\\n\\nLeaving this ticket open as requested — obsoletion of GO:0045550 to be handled separately.\\n\\n`make travis_build` passes.\\n\\n---\\n🤖 **Generated by @dragon-ai-agent**\\n- Model: `claude-opus-4-7`\\n- Agent harness: claude-code\\n- Triggered by: @raymond91125\\n- Run: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25065339565)\",\n48:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T16:53:21Z\",\n49:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n50:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n51:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n52:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n53:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963#issuecomment-4337370681\",\n54:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n55:     },\n56:     {\n57:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAqaEDg\",\n58:       \"author\": {\n59:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n60:       },\n61:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n62:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please obsolete GO:0045550.\",\n63:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T22:07:35Z\",\n64:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n65:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n66:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n67:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n68:         {\n69:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n70:           \"users\": {\n71:             \"totalCount\": 1\n72:           }\n73:         }\n74:       ],\n75:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963#issuecomment-4339434510\",\n76:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n77:     },\n78:     {\n79:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAqaLLg\",\n80:       \"author\": {\n81:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n82:       },\n83:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n84:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25080190865)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n85:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T22:07:56Z\",\n86:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n87:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n88:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n89:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n90:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963#issuecomment-4339436334\",\n91:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n92:     }\n93:   ],\n94:   \"title\": \"Obsolete GO:0045550 geranylgeranyl reductase activity\",\n95:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963\"\n96: }\n\n(End of file - total 96 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"This term has no enzyme xref:\\n\\nid: GO:0045550\\nname: geranylgeranyl reductase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the formation of phytyl group from the stepwise reduction of a geranylgeranyl group.\\\" [PMID:9492312]\\nis_a: GO:0016491 ! oxidoreductase activity\\n\\nPMID:9492312 abstract says:\\n\\\"Geranylgeranyl reductase expressed in Escherichia coli sequentially catalyzes the reduction of geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlorophyll a as well as the reduction of free geranylgeranyl diphosphate into phytyl diphosphate.\\\"\\n