{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778982476331,"sessionID":"ses_1cc61f63cffe3JDoCmXU5s6B5T","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_uTqlfKpyrYqqGenlYj1wt5zO","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"obo-grep.pl --noheader -r 'id: GO:0045550|id: GO:0102067|GO:0045550' src/ontology/go-edit.obo","timeout":120000,"workdir":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go","description":"Inspect relevant GO term stanzas"},"output":"[Term]\nid: GO:0045550\nname: geranylgeranyl reductase activity\nnamespace: molecular_function\ndef: \"Catalysis of the formation of phytyl group from the stepwise reduction of a geranylgeranyl group.\" [PMID:9492312]\nis_a: GO:0016491 ! oxidoreductase activity\n\n[Term]\nid: GO:0102067\nname: geranylgeranyl diphosphate reductase activity\nnamespace: molecular_function\ndef: \"Catalysis of the reaction: phytyl diphosphate + 3 NADP+ = geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H+. This enzyme also catalyzes the reduction of geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlorophyll a.\" [EC:1.3.1.83, PMID:9492312, RHEA:26229]\nxref: EC:1.3.1.83 {source=\"skos:exactMatch\"}\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-10625\nxref: RHEA:26229 {source=\"skos:exactMatch\"}\nis_a: GO:0016628 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-CH group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30193\" xsd:anyURI\n\n","metadata":{"output":"[Term]\nid: GO:0045550\nname: geranylgeranyl reductase activity\nnamespace: molecular_function\ndef: \"Catalysis of the formation of phytyl group from the stepwise reduction of a geranylgeranyl group.\" [PMID:9492312]\nis_a: GO:0016491 ! oxidoreductase activity\n\n[Term]\nid: GO:0102067\nname: geranylgeranyl diphosphate reductase activity\nnamespace: molecular_function\ndef: \"Catalysis of the reaction: phytyl diphosphate + 3 NADP+ = geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H+. This enzyme also catalyzes the reduction of geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlor